I think this is because prod isn't hooked up to the SCSB production bucket yet (didn't want to push partner updates out from these boxes.)

See https://github.com/pulibrary/princeton_ansible/blob/c7bce40ad04daa1048ff84a89d4803bae18f6998/group_vars/bibdata/alma_production.yml#L97-L102

vs 

https://github.com/pulibrary/princeton_ansible/blob/c7bce40ad04daa1048ff84a89d4803bae18f6998/group_vars/bibdata/production.yml#L127-L134

yes I see what you are saying. That it is disabled so that we dont submit princeton files to recap.
